{"tid":1544090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你哋香港人老母 包括我自己","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:02:39.000Z","uid":73959,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f55af969067260459369583a972cf79caf26a865","tid":1544090,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"屌警察先<br />\n政見唔同唔緊要<br />\n但已經發展到仇恨市民、行私刑<br />\n前線嗰班痴哂線所以我都費事屌<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係前線嗰班唔好以為唔關你事</span><br />\n我就係屌你哋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔信你唔知情 冇料爆</span><br />\n你為求自保自我滅聲=岀賣香港人<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n再屌黨鐵<br />\n你班黨鐵狗 係呀你哋都係狗<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">特別坐office同station control嗰啲呀 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔信你唔知情 冇料爆</span><br />\n你為求自保自我滅聲=岀賣香港人<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n跟手屌消防<br />\n我仍然尊敬部分嘅消防<br />\n好可惜 一窩靚粥被啲老鼠屎整臭哂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">831啲消防我唔信你唔知情 冇料爆</span><br />\n你為求自保自我滅聲=岀賣香港人<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n再屌醫護<br />\n同上 我仍然尊敬部分嘅醫護<br />\n好可惜 一窩靚粥被啲老鼠屎整臭哂<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">831你話唔知有冇死人 咁強姦呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔信全部人都唔知情 冇料爆</span><br />\n你為求自保自我滅聲=岀賣香港人<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n再屌所有同政府合作嘅承辦商/公司<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫政府寫人面辨識系統program堆仆街<br />\n一直以嚟啲大白象工程 幫手做假數堆audit</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你哋係咪香港人呀？</span><br />\n你為求自保自我滅聲=岀賣香港人<br />\n我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n最後我屌埋自己老母呀<br />\n我從來冇出去發夢<br />\n因為我自私我懦弱<br />\n最多係遊下行做下文宣<br />\n其他乜撚都冇付出過呀<br />\n<br />\n全世界最唔能夠屌係前線同文宣<br />\n點解呀？<br />\n因為你哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連最簡單爆黑幕都唔撚做</span></span>嘅時候<br />\n班<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">前線係岀面幫你擋子彈</span></span>呀！<br />\n班文宣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不停岀post不停cap圖整合</span></span>做到黑眼圈都岀哂嚟！<br />\n但你班<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&rdquo;香港人&rdquo;</span></strong></span>仲<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">日日係不同崗位為呢個政權做嘢</span></span></strong> 傷害自己人<br />\n有時我都覺得自己唔配有民主<br />\n因為我冇做啲咩特別嘢去爭取<br />\n但最無資格係你班<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">知情不報</span></strong></span><br />\n甘願為咗份工而包庇呢個政府嘅垃圾！"},{"pid":"d8253901e071662909c00420a7a8ddae5c291de3","tid":1544090,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f25968d0269a9ef741a19131c7bcc1581ac43b24","tid":1544090,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:13:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［幫手推到置頂］9月8日 美領人鏈防鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544032</a><br />\n跪求各位巴絲幫手推一推<del>（我係一個有夢想既P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 